## Summary
Amplitude's Insights feature uses Prophet machine learning to detect anomalies in product data through automatic, custom, and smart alerts that can be configured for Event Segmentation and Funnel Analysis charts with daily or hourly frequency, with notifications deliverable via email or Slack channels.

